dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Door County, WI 2017
dc_description_s: These line data layers represent roads and right of ways (ROW) for Door County, Wisconsin in 2017. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, Door_Transportation_ROW_2017.gdb. Features included in the geodatabase are 'DOOR_ROADS_2017' and 'DOOR_ROW_2017'.[Road/Street Centerline network of Door County, Wisconsin]
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
